      "Text": "Security update for xorg-x11-server",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for xorg-x11-server fixes the following issue\n\n- CVE-2026-55999: missing bounds check in `glamor_font_get` can lead to a heap buffer overflow when a font loaded from\n  a malicious PCF file is processed (bsc#1268893).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
